(13, 'Tresor Bay View Junior Suite', '<p>This room offers an extra large bed and spacious sitting area equipped with a 32-inch LCD TV, iPod docking station and work desk. The marble bathroom features a bathtub or shower and includes a bathrobe and toiletries.</p><p><br /></p>', '107', '128,127,124,120,119,115', 300.00, 10, 46.00, 3, 4, 5, '97,96,94,93,91,90', 7, 1, 'publish', '2021-03-25 03:26:14', '2021-03-25 03:26:51'),
